---
title: Thai Style Fish Soup with Mushrooms, Carrot and Cashews
description: Our 20-minute twist on this classic Thai broth is the perfect thing for busy evenings. Delicate white fish, fresh herbs, red Thai curry paste, lime and fresh vegetables are gently combined in a warming noodle soup before being topped with cashews and chopped coriander for a layer of delicious texture Fresh, zesty, light and comforting, our Tom Yum soup is a guaranteed dinner winner.
